\id TIT - Zanaki Titus 
\h Tito 
\toc3 Tito 
\toc2 Tito 
\toc1 Enyaarubha ya Pauro ku Tito 
\mt2 Enyaarubha ya Pauro ku 
\mt1 Tito 
\imt1 Obhutaangiro 
\ip Eriingʼaara rino, rikaamirwe no omweega Pauro. Hano yaari akyaari kukaama eriingʼaara rino, Pauro yaari arakora emirimo gya Taatabhugya hamwe na Tito mukigiinga kya Kirete. Kyaamwe akarwa eyo, akamara siku suuhu, akamukaamira Tito eriingʼaara rino kwo obhuswaagyo bhwoosi iguru yo okwiimeererera abhiikirirya Kirete eyo. 
\ip Munyaarubha yino, Pauro akamuha Tito emirimo gyo okusora abhakaruka bhe ekanisa. Kweeki akamutoongera okubhatugika abhiikirirya bha Kirete, kwo okubha bhaari bharimu abheegya bho orurimi. Pauro aramutoongera Tito na kyeego okukaangata amahizo mukanisa, abhakaruka, abhamura na abhabhagati. Mubhuteero aramuhiitya Tito kubha Abhakrisito bhoosi bhiikare kwo omureembe no obhusaambaaruku, na bhatabha bhaatu bho okurwaana no okutwaanikana amahizo. 
\c 1  
\s1 Obhukeerya 
\p  
\v 1 Enyaarubha yino nikaamiri enye Pauro, omugya wa Taatabhugya, kweeki omweega wa Yeesu Krisito. Nitumirwe kwiiguru yo okweerekeererya abhaatu bhano bhasorirwe na Taatabhugya, okubha bhasakiribhwe okumenya obhuheene iguru wa Yeesu Krisito. Obhuheene bhuyo bhurabhakaangatya okumuseengera Taatabhugya,  
\v 2 no okubhaha obhwiisige bhwo obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego. Taatabhugya akaragirira obhuhoru bhuyo, hano yaari akyaari kuteema ekyaaro, ewe atakunagya kugaamba orurimi.  
\v 3 Bhoono, eriibhaga rino rikungʼarira niryo Taatabhugya Omutuurya weetu yeerekirye kubhweero Amangʼana gaaye Amazomu gayo, na aswaagirye nirwaaze amangʼana gayo.  
\v 4 Ndakukaamira awe Tito, omwaana waane we eheene mubhwiikirirya bhuno tukwiisanginia hamwe. 
\p Orubhaango no omureembe okurwa ku Taatabhugya Taata na ku Krisito Yeesu Omutuurya weetu, bhibhe naawe. 
\s1 Emirimo gya Tito mukigiinga kya Kirete 
\p  
\v 5 Hano narwiiri Kirete eyo, nikakutiga awe okubha otuure kisi amangʼana agaandi gano gasaagiri, hamwe no okusora abhakaruka bhe ekanisa mumigye gyoosi, kyeego nakuswaagirye. 
\p  
\v 6 Omukaruka wowoosi we ekanisa, areenderwa kubha muutu wuno atana amasoro gogoosi. Areenderwa abhe omuheene kumukari waaye,\f + \fr 1:6 \fk Abhe omuheene kumukari waaye\ft , ku Kiyunaani ni \fqa abhe akweeriri mukari wumwe.\f* abhaana bhaaye bhabhe abhiikirirya, bhatabha abhazabhuri kisya bhano bhatakumwiigwa.  
\v 7 Omukaangati we ekanisa wuyo, areenderwa kubha muutu wuno atana amasoro gogoosi, kwo okubha ni mwiimeerereri we emirimo gya Taatabhugya. Atabha muutu muregenu, omururu, omunywi omuraara, omurwaani, kweeki atabha ne enaamba embiihu yo okubhona eziimbirya.  
\v 8 Nawe abhe omuginihya, aseegiri amazomu, abhe na kusuuhu, omuheene, muhoreeru, na wuno akwiibhaaha.  
\v 9 Abhe aragwaata bhuzomu amangʼana go obhuheene iguru wa Yeesu Krisito, kyeego akeegibhwa. Hayo niho, akunagya okugumirya abhaatu kumeegyo go obhuheene, no okubheerekeererya bhano bhakwaanga ameegyo gayo. 
\p  
\v 10 Nirakubhuurira ego, kwo okubha Kirete hayo bhaari bhariho abhaatu bhaaru bhano bhatakwiigwa, bharabhuga amangʼana gano gatana bhweera, kweeki ni bhakaangirirya, kiindi abhamwe bhano bharwiiri munyaangi ya Abhayahudi. Abhaatu bhayo bharekibhwe okweegya,  
\v 11 kwo okubha bharabhurya abhaatu muziinyuumba nzaru. Bhareegya amangʼana gano gatakweenderwa, okubha bhabhone eziimbirya kuteemo embiihu.  
\v 12 Ekare haari no omurooti wumwe Mukirete, wo waabhu abheene, wuno yabhugiri, “Abhakirete ni bhabheehi eziisiku zoosi, ni kye ebhityeenyi ebhibhi, bhasoohu na abhatobhu!”  
\v 13 Obhugaambi bhuyo ni bhwe eheene. Kweego, obhe orabharekya bhukongʼu abhaatu bhayo, okubha bhagwaate ameegyo go obhuheene.  
\v 14 Bhatige okwiitegeerera amagano ge Ekiyahudi gano gatana obhweera, no obhuswaagyo bhwa abhaatu bhano bhatigiri obhuheene. 
\p  
\v 15 Kubhaatu bhe eziikoro nzomu embere wa Taatabhugya, ebhigiro bhyoosi bhyeeriibhwe. Nawe, kubhaatu makire na bhano bhatari abhiikirirya, ebhigiro bhyoosi ni makire, kwo okubha amiiseego gaabhu ne emitima gyaabhu, giizwiiri amakire.  
\v 16 Bharabhuga abheene bharamumenya Taatabhugya, nawe amahokya gaabhu gareerekya kubha bharamwaanga. Bhayo nibho abhazabhuri, bhatakungʼarira kwe engʼana yoyoosi enzomu. 
\c 2  
\s1 Ameegyo go obhuheene 
\p  
\v 1 Nawe awe Tito, obhe oreegya abhaatu kuriingʼaana na ameegyo go obhuheene.  
\v 2 Obhabhuurire abhakaruka bhabhe na kusuuhu, bho obhusuuku na bhano bhakwiibhaaha. Kweeki, bhabhe no obhwiikirirya bhwe eheene, bhabhe no obhuseegi no obhwiikongʼeererya. 
\p  
\v 3 Egoego na abhakiikuru nabho, obhabhuurire kubha bhabhe ne eteemwa yino ekumuguungya Taatabhugya. Bhatabha abhamoonyi, bhatabha abhanywi abharaara, nawe bhareenderwa okweegya ameegyo ge esiira enzomu,  
\v 4 okubha bhabhe bharabheegya abhaakya kubhaseega abhasubhe bhaabhu na abhaana bhaabhu.  
\v 5 Kweeki, bhabhe bharabheegya kubha na kusuuhu, bhabhe ne ekoro nzomu, bhakore bhuzomu emirimo muziinyuumba zyaabhu, bhabhe bhazomu na bhano bhakusuuka abhasubhe bhaabhu. Obhabhuurire bhakore ego, okubha engʼana ya Taatabhugya etazeerwa. 
\p  
\v 6 Egoego na abhamura, obharekye bhabhe na kusuuhu.  
\v 7 Naawe, mumangʼana goosi, obhe ekireengyo kyo okweegwa kweebho kwo okukora amazomu. Obhe omuheene no omugumiru mumeegyo gaazo.  
\v 8 Ameegyo gaazo gabhe ge eheene na gatabha na amasoro kubhaatu. Naabhe omuutu areenda kugahakana, arasuukibhwa, kwo okubha atakubha ne engʼana yo okutugaamba bhubhi. 
\p  
\v 9 Kweeki abhagya nabho, obhabhuurire kubha bhabhasuuke abhakuru bhaabhu mugoosi, bhabhasaambaarukye, na bhatahakana nabho.  
\v 10 Bhatabha bhiibhi, nawe bhabhe abhaheene, okubha emirimo gyaabhu gyoosi, gikore abhaatu bharutwe na ameegyo ga Taatabhugya Omutuurya weetu. 
\p  
\v 11 Obhe oreegya amangʼana gayo, kwo okubha Taatabhugya abheerekirye orubhaango rwaaye, kwo okureeta obhutuurya kubhaatu bhoosi.  
\v 12 Orubhaango ruyo, ruratweegya okwaanga obhubhi ne enaamba ye ekyaaro. Kweego, hano tukyaari mukyaaro kino, tubhe na kusuuhu, bhe eheene, na abhaatu bhano bhakwiikara obhwiikari bhwo okumuseengera Taatabhugya.  
\v 13 Twiikare ego, eriibhaga rino tukwiisigira orusiku rwo orubhaango, hano Yeesu Krisito araakyoore arorekane mubhuguungo bhwaaye. Ewe niwe Taatabhugya weetu Omukuru no Omutuurya weetu.  
\v 14 Akiiruusya kwiiguru weetu, okubha atutuurye okurwa mubhibhi bhyoosi. Akeenda okutweerya, okubha tubhe abhaatu bhaaye bhe eheene, bhano bhakwiiruusya okukora amazomu. 
\p  
\v 15 Ambe bhoono, obhe oreegya amangʼana gayo goosi. Oheerwe obhuturo bhwoosi bhwo okugumirya no okurekya abhaatu. Kweego, otazeerwa na muutu wowoosi. 
\c 3  
\s1 Okukora amazomu 
\p  
\v 1 Obhe orabhahiitya abhaatu kubha, bhabhe bharasuuka no okwiigwa abhakaangati na bho obhunagya. Bhabhe bhiibhanwiiri okukora amangʼana goosi amazomu.  
\v 2 Obhabhuurire bhatatuka muutu wowoosi, bhatabha bhatiindi, bhabhe bhanyoohu na abhasuuku kubhaatu bhoosi. 
\p  
\v 3 Naabhe etwe abheene twaari bhageege na tutaari tumenyiri amangʼana ga Taatabhugya, abhaangi na tukaangiririibhwe, eno tubheeri abhagya bhe eziinaamba mbiihu zya tuubho nzaru. Obhwiikari bhweetu bhwaari bhubhi no omugono. Abhaatu bhaari bharatubhiihirirya, neetwe twaari turabhabhiihirirya.  
\v 4 Nawe Taatabhugya, Omutuurya weetu, akatweerekya obhuzomu no obhuseegi bhwaaye, akatutuurya.  
\v 5 Atatutuurirye kwe ekigirirye kya amahokya geetu amazomu, nawe kwe ekigirirye kye ebhigoongi bhyaaye. Atweerirye ebhibhi bhyeetu, kuyo nikwo okwiibhurwa bhuhya. Kweeki atuheeri obhwiikari bhuhya kwo okuhitira Ekoro Muhoreeru.\f + \fr 3:5 \fk Ekoro Muhoreeru\ft . Rora amangʼana gano mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* 
\v 6 Taatabhugya akatwiikirya Ekoro Muhoreeru, kwo okuhitira Yeesu Krisito Omutuurya weetu.  
\v 7 Akakora ego, no okutubhara kubha bhe eheene kwe enzira yo orubhaango rwaaye, okubha tubhone okugabha obhuhoru bhwa kirakeego, kyeego tukwiisiga. 
\p  
\v 8 Amangʼana gayo ni ge eheene. Ndeenda awe ogakumiirirye, okubha bhoosi bhano bhamwiikiriirye Taatabhugya, bhagagwaatirire no okubha no omukya kukora amazomu. Amangʼana gayo ni mazomu, kweeki gano obhweera kubhaatu bhoosi.  
\v 9 Nawe, wiiriihe no obhuhakani bhwe ekigeege, obhuzaabhi bhwa amariina ga bhazaazi, eriiyoge no obhuhakani iguru we emigiro gya Musa. Gayo goosi gatana bhweera bhwobhwoosi.  
\v 10 Omuutu wuno akutwaanikania abhaatu, omurekye orugeendo rwo okutaanga kisya rwa kabhiri. Hano okubhona atakwiigwa, tigana neewe.  
\v 11 Omenyiri kubha omuutu kya wuyo atigiri obhuheene, ni muutu wuno akukora ebhibhi, yiitiniiri ekiina omweene. 
\s1 Amangʼana go obhuteero 
\p  
\v 12 Ndabhatuma Aritema kasi Tikiko kwaawe. Hano araahike owaazo, okore omukya ombone mumugye gwa Nikapori. Niendiri kwiikara eyo eriibhaga rye embeho.  
\v 13 Okore omukya kumusakirya Zena, omukaari we emigiro, na Apooro. Obhahe bhyoosi bhyo okubhasakirya munzira, bhatasuuhirwa kigiro.  
\v 14 Abhiikirirya abharikyeetu nabho, bheege okukora amazomu kwo omukya, okubha bhasakirye bhano bhakweenda obhweendi bhwe eheene. Bharaakore ego, obhwiikari bhwaabhu bhurabha no obhweera. 
\p  
\v 15 Abhaatu bhoosi bhano bhari hamwe neenye, bharakukeerya. Bhoono naawe woosi, obhakeerye abhaseegwa bheetu mubhwiikirirya. 
\p Orubhaango rwa Taatabhugya rubhe hamwe neemwe mwoosi.